						               													<description>Rediscover the power of your imagination as you take on the role  of a storyteller. Use the Bimba Cards to interpret phrases in your own unique way. Then convince your fellow players that your interpretation is the most meaningful. Score points for every vote you get and every vote you can sway in your favour. You win if you have the highest number of points at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Play..&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player is dealt with 5 cards and as game begins, One player picks a phrase card and reads it out to the other players,&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each other player selects the card in their hands that best matches the phrase and gives the selected card to the dealer, without showing it to the others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The dealer shuffles the cards with all the received cards. All pictures are shown face up and every player votes for the cards that best suits the phrase. They cannot vote for their own card. Then one of the player challenges the votes and tries to convince the others about why another card is better suited and pitch for it. Players can tell stories, bring out instances to convince the other players to change their votes. The challenger scores one pink token for every vote they turn in their favour.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players score points for every vote for their own card and collects the tokens.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Apart from the phrase cards, players can opt to create their own Stories, Verse, Phrase or a word. If they win this round, they get an additional 20 points apart from the votes. &amp;#10;The game ends when the deck is empty or when the players decide to end the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The base game and all expansions have 84 main Bimba cards each with phrase cards, Vote cards, 1 play mat, 84 winning tokens and 1 Rule book.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
